OL,6,FFinlay MacDonald has been found guilty
OL,7,Fof murdering his brother-in-law and
OL,8,Fjailed for 28 years, ITV News Scotland
OL,9,FReporter Louise Scott reports
OL,11,FA father of four has been found guilty
OL,12,Fof the murder of his brother in law in
OL,13,Fa shooting rampage on the Isle of Skye
OL,14,Fin August 2022.
OL,16,FFinlay MacDonald, 41, was further
OL,17,Ffound guilty of three counts of
OL,18,Fattempted murder, including of against
OL,19,Fwife.
